'''Abeṛṛay''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''Felis silvestris'') d [[tiserɣuda|aserɣud]] meẓẓiyen yeṭṭafaren [[tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] n [[Amcic (tawsit)|umcic]] yettidir seg [[Turuft|Uruppa]] d [[Tafriqt|Tefrikt]] ar [[Amalu n Asya|umalu n Asya]], Abeṛṛay d [[aẓaṛ amezday|aẓaṛ agejdan]] n [[amcic|yimcac]] [[agrad|imegruden]] (imcac yettidiren ar ufgan) yakk ass-a, Akken iga d [[agmar|anegmar]] igerrzen i kra n [[talmest|telmas]] n [[Timseɣẓaẓ|temseɣẓaẓ]] d [[aylal|iylalen]] <br />
Llan-t waṭas n [[tadfert|tdefrin]] deg telmest-a yettidiren deg idgan yemgaraden n 3 n [[amenẓaw|imenẓawen-a]]

Seg tserɣuda id yettilin s waṭas i wbeṛṛay d [[Areksim]] yettidiren s tuget deg [[Taneẓruft|tneẓrufin]]

== Aglam ==
[[Azuk]] n [[tawtemt|tewtemt]] n ubeṛṛay yettili gar n 2,7 ar 4 kg. Ma d [[awtem]] yettawaṭ seg 4 ar 5 kg, Maca azuk-a yezmer ad yemgarad s unect (ɛla ḥsab) n tilin n tgemrawin s tuget neɣ s tdersi 

Ini n ubeṛṛay d win yettilin d aras imal ar uzunɣid 

